explanation: Binary search the answer (length L). For each L, use DP to check if we can break every stable subarray longer than L with ≤ maxC changes. DP[i] = min changes to make prefix i valid. For each i, look back at most L positions, track GCD, and update DP[i] if GCD ≥ 2. Complexity is O(n log n log A) where A is max value.

